I'll definitely make this again. Is really good

Rating: 3
This is a good recipe considering how quick and easy it is and how few ingredients are involved -- great for a decent, guest-worthy meal when on a budget or short on time. However, I felt that something was lacking. The orange flavor was overpowered by the prosciutto, so I sprinkled on the remaining zest. Next time I will add the entire zest to the sauce, as well as some extra orange juice. I might also try stirring in some of the pulp or topping with some small orange slices.

